{"tid":1632684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有仲係和理非既同我入黎我正式宣佈 10.7 全民三罷籌備日唔係今個月內就會輸","createTime":"2019-10-06T19:53:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T20:16:52.000Z","uid":121001,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"131d6267a76b1b6b1279809946e3f0b4ebcb41ae","tid":1632684,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:53:03.000Z","msg":"10.4 去到 10.6<br />\n勇武不斷打爆商店玻璃，地鐵站，私了<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反效果</span></span></span>出哂黎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 國際一向係支持和理非既香港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n林鄭 10.4 用緊急法立蒙面法，係故意激起民怨，然後比接兵不動，班狗係冇即時作出任何執法行為，目的係要喺國際上幫林鄭攞籌碼，製造真暴動，好暴力既場面，咁樣班狗再行動就係正義。<br />\n星期五六日我地已經<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">比哂子彈同籌碼</span></span>林鄭，再咁落起我地國際戰線都會輸<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. 淺黃係會浮走喺淺藍同中立之間</span></span><br />\n勇武既行為係會嚇怕堆淺黃，當你叫大遊行既時候，淺黃同勇武一齊行，班狗突襲咬到就咬，拉到就拉。對普通人黎講，破壞商舖同爆竊一樣。佢地係有機會同勇武義士食同一條罪。淺黃和理非驚就唔會出黎。加上淺黃睇片會好支持，但<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冇機會比和理非實際行動</span></span>，最後冇人back up勇武，場比賽又會輸。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3. 損兵折將</span></span><br />\n次次勇武出黎都拎成身gear周街走，唔單止好易比狗逗，明哲保身仲要棄gear。都唔係話平架。加上每次睇番班狗吠既記錄，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">平均勇武出黎一次就要承受一百人被捕</span></span>。比人拉左仲要被控好多條罪，值得損失咁多義士咩？再諗深一層，點解會損失義士？因為班和理非仲未夠團結，一次全民三罷都未做得好好睇睇。假如全民三罷做得好既，罷一星期係可以保到七百個手足。多你一個真係好多。如果勇武比人拉哂，冇人backup 和理非，最後都係會輸。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">4. buy time</span></span> <br />\n國際戰線做緊野架啦，法庭司法覆核做緊野架啦。依兩條可能贏既戰線係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">需要等，需要耐性，需要時間</span></strong></span>。全民三罷可以話係我地用最低成本但又拖到最長時間既抗爭方法。美國法案要通過，起碼再等幾星期。司法覆核要成功，都要開庭同上訴，起碼都一星期。唔好同我講咩等唔切就做哂衝衝子，最後比哂子彈人地支持佢既決定，下面有條rthk 既 link 可以睇到我到係確確實實中計，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">比哂彈藥對家</span></span>，你話我中計黨我都係咁話。等唔切，林鄭最怕既法案過唔到，司法覆核唔到。又輸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484656-20191006.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484656-20191006.htm&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEpqZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=280fc295\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484656-20191006.htm&h=996a7dba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484656-20191006.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以<br />\n我正式宣佈 <br />\n10.7 全民三罷籌備日<br />\n唔係今個月內就會輸</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d71025f54d01326aae07cc140d2650bbe22322","tid":1632684,"uid":47149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:55:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"376b560658f3adcac43ae8f217c3302a55f7dfb8","tid":1632684,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:56:07.000Z","msg":"自推十次<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全民三罷</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca63feed261da0df4deef88368156efcbb4d7a8","tid":1632684,"uid":121001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,